          (MX (\GETBASEFLOATP BASE 0)))
         [for I from 0 to (SUB1 CNT) do (if [NOT (GREATERP MX (\GETBASEFLOATP BASE (IPLUS I I]
                                            then (SETQ IDX I)
                                                 (SETQ MX (\GETBASEFLOATP BASE (IPLUS IDX IDX]
         IDX])

(\BLKFMIN.UFN
